result.title: Resmed Receives FDA Clearance for Personalized Therapy Comfort Settings, to be Marketed as Smart Comfort, an AI-Enabled, Digital Medical Device That Helps Personalize CPAP Therapy
result.text: SAN DIEGO, Dec. 08, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Resmed (NYSE: RMD, ASX: RMD), the leading health technology company focused on sleep, breathing and care delivered in the home, today announced it has received U.S. Food and Drug Administration (FDA) clearance for Personalized Therapy Comfort Settings (PTCS), to be marketed as Smart Comfort. Smart Comfort is the first FDA-cleared AI-enabled medical device that recommends personalized comfort settings to help people with obstructive sleep apnea (OSA) start and stay on CPAP therapy.
